# 1. Ignore absolutely everything by default
*

# 2. Allow Git to scan ALL directories/subdirectories so it can find the nested "Sub-" folders
!*/
!**/

# 3. Whitelist your root-level files and assets
!index.html
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!assets/*

# 4. Lock down everything inside regular directories, EXCEPT for "Sub-" folders
/**/*
!**/Sub-*/

# 5. Whitelist only the HTML and title files inside those "Sub-" folders
!**/Sub-*/**/*.html
!**/Sub-*/title.txt

# 6. Specific overrides for folders you want completely blocked
kubernetes/
save.html
